gmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鑑於全球各地的2019冠狀病毒病個案數字持續及迅速上升所引致的健康風險，香港特別行政區政府基於公共衞生考慮，今日（三月十七日）決定對所有海外國家／屬地發出紅色外遊警示。"},{"pid":"20755acf3e4b8ea7171eb12e4f9a08b76481aaa6","tid":1930059,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d5e29387c2c4edcdeb78e70deb2fd6b92e599c9","tid":1930059,"uid":103783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:05:01.000Z","msg":"朱敏健手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:21:58.000Z","msg":"啲尿好黃"},{"pid":"75f03d46f3b3954a0ad7b5b80cc639ddd997ab1c","tid":1930059,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1300e8a58ab18b34cd39de6211887da32d5348b","tid":1930059,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:09:28.000Z","msg":"條友鳩噏能力算高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b1b929793924eedaebc99b78786d86e40e59d31","tid":1930059,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0cecd5ce81a498c746cc2c670127cd9ea8d7a9","tid":1930059,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4b00c58343d2d8c664600d6ef0ead9032331b7c","tid":1930059,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03e314fe4fa59548a9dcfd96c329baba8c6cea38","tid":1930059,"uid":47279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:02:07.000Z","msg":"叫佢告撚左林鄭岐視先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鑑於全球各地的2019冠狀病毒病個案數字持續及迅速上升所引致的健康風險，香港特別行政區政府基於公共衞生考慮，今日（三月十七日）決定對所有海外國家／屬地發出紅色外遊警示。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:23:48.000Z","msg":"告未"},{"pid":"f67811f0b8a7e82a1870b691fc03a6373c233763","tid":1930059,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:13:56.000Z","msg":"平機會已接獲近<span style=\"color: red;\">600宗</span>涉及歧視的投訴和查詢，主要有關餐廳拒絕招待內地客及講普通話人士，相信數字仍會再上升。他解釋，<span style=\"color: red;\">出於防疫原因不招待屬於有合理需要，不屬於殘疾歧視</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，平機會暫時亦未接獲有關投訴。<br />\n<br />\n朱敏健表示，食肆不接待說普通話人士佔最多投訴，也有酒店拒絕招待說普通話人士或醫護人員。他指具體個案要逐一審視，即使涉及歧視行為，有合理需要亦可豁免。如果被投訴的商戶，只表明不招待說普通話人士，未必構成殘疾和種族歧視，因語言不是種族歧視的選項，但若不招待內地人卻招待同樣說普通話的馬來西亞人，便可能涉及歧視。他又舉例如果華人和歐美人士，只是不招待華人，投訴可能成立。<br />\n<br />\n他說，平機會一般會先聯絡投訴人和被投訴人，了解詳情，再向他們解釋法例並勸喻食肆收回涉歧視字眼的告示，希望盡快平息事件。他呼籲，大家不應執著抗拒哪些人，應齊心應付疫情。"}]}